## My personal zathura

## Settings
set adjust-open         width
set window-width        1500
set window-height       1000
set scroll-full-overlap 0.05
set selection-clipboard clipboard

## Inverted mode
set recolor-keephue
set recolor-darkcolor  "#DCDCCC"
set recolor-lightcolor "#1F1F1F"

## Alternative color settings

# set recolor-darkcolor  "#E0E0E0" 
# set recolor-lightcolor "#151515" 
# set recolor-darkcolor  "#93A1A1"
# set recolor-lightcolor "#002B36"

## Mappings
map [normal]     <BackSpace> scroll full-up
map [fullscreen] <BackSpace> scroll full-up
map [normal]     i           set recolor
map [fullscreen] i           set recolor
map [normal]     <C-m>       feedkeys ":bmark "
map [fullscreen] <C-m>       feedkeys ":bmark "
map [normal]     d           scroll half-down    ## this mapping overwrites d for
map [fullscreen] d           scroll half-down    ## toggling dual page display
map [normal]     D           toggle_page_mode
map [fullscreen] D           toggle_page_mode
map [normal]     u           scroll half-up
map [fullscreen] u           scroll half-up
map [normal]     =           zoom in
map [fullscreen] =           zoom in
